{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x19143c",
      "back_en": "Esteemed sister, it seems the tea is ready.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido e tom formal preservados."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19146b",
      "back_en": "Hm. Ah... A delicious aroma.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1914ea",
      "back_en": "rarity. The cost was high, but it was worth every coin.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19155d",
      "back_en": "Your approval is my justification.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'justificação' cobre 'vindication'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1915b1",
      "back_en": "...So... what are you two doing here, exactly?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191612",
      "back_en": "and Ougi there 'piling on wood' as if they owned the place.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'metendo lenha' não traduz 'lounging around'; perde sentido de ociosidade."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191753",
      "back_en": "To reject us now... What a heartless man!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1919c7",
      "back_en": "didn't hear news from Oshtor.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191aca",
      "back_en": "by his side, we can accomplish much.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191e02",
      "back_en": "CLOSE to this guy...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191e9d",
      "back_en": "all that 'resurrecting your noble house' thing?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x191fdf",
      "back_en": "put that future beyond our reach.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1920a2",
      "back_en": "But! There's no reason to lose hope!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19221e",
      "back_en": "Sounds like she's getting big/large.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'grandona' = física; 'big head' = ficar convencida/arrogante."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1923ac",
      "back_en": "What wonderful news! Right, Haku?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1925c5",
      "back_en": "I'm afraid the others won't accompany us.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19274f",
      "back_en": "Hakurokaku are...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192761",
      "back_en": "Just the two of us.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'apenas' por 'yes', mas sentido contextual mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1928c4",
      "back_en": "I'm afraid I don't have great aptitude for",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1928f1",
      "back_en": "writing and calculation. Things... go (lisp style)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sotaque/lisp estilizado preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192980",
      "back_en": "To clarify... whenever I try, a dizziness (lisp)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Estilo de fala mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1929af",
      "back_en": "overwhelms me and I faint. (lisp)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel com lisp."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192a63",
      "back_en": "Splendid idea! My first patrol route should be (lisp)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192a95",
      "back_en": "through the gambling halls, since security tends to be (lisp)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192b48",
      "back_en": "Hmm... Is that so? Well, supposing it's what it is, (lisp)",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192c22",
      "back_en": "I'm afraid we must.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x192ebe",
      "back_en": "Yes, that's what Oshtor told us.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'nos disseram Oshtor' agramatical; deveria ser 'nos disse Oshtor'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x193101",
      "back_en": "Did you have some memories here?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Literal mas aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1931ad",
      "back_en": "Hahaha... So even you knew nothing.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19323e",
      "back_en": "To clarify, she means just the two of us.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1933c2",
      "back_en": "We prepared tea for you, Master.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x193408",
      "back_en": "Enjoy.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19359e",
      "back_en": "Thank you all for the warm welcome!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1936ba",
      "back_en": "Make yourself comfortable! No need for so much formality, Nosuri.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1937e7",
      "back_en": "Nosuri. I must ask your forgiveness.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1938d6",
      "back_en": "are nothing but a nuisance...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x194cda",
      "back_en": "Whoa--!? What the hell are you two doing!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Interjeição adaptada, ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x194d9d",
      "back_en": "We decided to keep you warm like this.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x194dc7",
      "back_en": "C-Completely naked...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195118",
      "back_en": "Your caring words bring us unimaginable joy.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195145",
      "back_en": "*Sigh* What the hell am I supposed to do?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'se supõe que eu faça' levemente truncado mas ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1951e2",
      "back_en": "It'd end up the same way as before...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195607",
      "back_en": "Are we of no use at all?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195619",
      "back_en": "Were we a burden to you, Master?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1957be",
      "back_en": "Are we a nuisance to you, Master?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19586e",
      "back_en": "defense daggers from their sheaths.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'self' implícito, aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19589f",
      "back_en": "We must be together with our Master.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1958f2",
      "back_en": "can't fulfill our purpose, we're unnecessary.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195952",
      "back_en": "raise the daggers to their throat.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195975",
      "back_en": "What--!? Hey, dammit, stop!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195b1e",
      "back_en": "killed themselves...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195d17",
      "back_en": "You have such inner warmth, Master.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x195d8f",
      "back_en": "Dammit, how did this come to this...?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'como isso chegou a isso' repetição desajeitada; preferir 'como chegou a isso'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1974e9",
      "back_en": "Wh-What the hell are you two trying to do!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19780b",
      "back_en": "full of secrets anyway.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1978d4",
      "back_en": "And that mysterious woman with him... Honoka.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x197b0b",
      "back_en": "Welcome, dear guest.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1980c7",
      "back_en": "That must have been a difficult ordeal for you...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19868d",
      "back_en": "Have you tasted those two yet?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Inuendo preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x198825",
      "back_en": "I imagine you haven't slept with either yet, right?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19890d",
      "back_en": "gives me the right to... DO... stuff with them.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x198ab0",
      "back_en": "If you ignore us like this, Master... death may come.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x198b30",
      "back_en": "delight.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x198bb9",
      "back_en": "It doesn't matter who this old man really is.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ab12",
      "back_en": "Haku... That wasn't expected of it.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Não era esperado disso' passivo/estranho; deveria ser 'Não esperava isso'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ae1a",
      "back_en": "How did it end up like this...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e41b",
      "back_en": "I thank you all for coming.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e4e5",
      "back_en": "than a meal that someone else is paying for.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e542",
      "back_en": "you. Please, enjoy as much as you like.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e5dc",
      "back_en": "be appreciated by those who truly esteem it.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e75f",
      "back_en": "and answers with all appearance of sincerity.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e7b8",
      "back_en": "bonds among dear friends?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e803",
      "back_en": "an Oshtor reason to me.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fragmento/trocadilho mantido literal."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19e881",
      "back_en": "a great deal, despite your appearance.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ea78",
      "back_en": "That's why I have such high hopes for you.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19eae5",
      "back_en": "Hail, Master Haku! Long have I dreamed of",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Estilo arcaico preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19eb4c",
      "back_en": "Wait, don't tell me HE'S the guy Oshtor was--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19eb7a",
      "back_en": "It was by honest Master Oshtor's invitation!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19eba7",
      "back_en": "I'm glad to await your leisure!",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'esperar seu lazer' literal demais; sentido é 'a seu dispor/quando lhe convier'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ec99",
      "back_en": "So that I may better ensure the fullness of",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ecc9",
      "back_en": "your cup, master!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ed35",
      "back_en": "Oh, if I could, master, but such obedience",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'obeisance' = reverência/mesura, não 'obediência'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19ed69",
      "back_en": "would be discourteous, ah, for my present... offices...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'would ill become' ~ 'seria descortês', aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19f2a7",
      "back_en": "Yes. Public... and other.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19f2f8",
      "back_en": "knows Oshtor and Ukon are the same person?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19f5ea",
      "back_en": "I came here for a much bigger reason than that.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19f62b",
      "back_en": "It's about you, Haku. You don't realize it, but",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x19f65d",
      "back_en": "your worth is far more than you could ever imagine.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a00ec",
      "back_en": "A moment ago? That doesn't sound like \"admiration\"...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'gazing' = contemplar/observar, não 'admiração'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0164",
      "back_en": "It's fine, Haku. It seems my dear brother owes",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0239",
      "back_en": "If you know about Ukon's identity, I imagine",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0267",
      "back_en": "you're not just a vendor, right?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Omite 'candy'; 'né verdade' desajeitado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a02b3",
      "back_en": "Oho...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0335",
      "back_en": "So, you would know of my connection to Oshtor,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a036d",
      "back_en": "Sakon's voice suddenly changes.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a03c1",
      "back_en": "person...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a03f5",
      "back_en": "Instead, his voice is icy, with a hint of menace.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a044a",
      "back_en": "Maybe this reveals the truth you seek.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0716",
      "back_en": "Heh heh heh...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0725",
      "back_en": "L-Lord Mikazuchi...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0757",
      "back_en": "That's... Mikazuchi!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a079f",
      "back_en": "to think you'd never figure it out.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a084c",
      "back_en": "a deathly smirk spreading across his face.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a08d1",
      "back_en": "Business as usual.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Negócio de sempre' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a08e4",
      "back_en": "Is that... really you, Mikazuchi?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0a40",
      "back_en": "So what is the purpose of all this?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0ac4",
      "back_en": "the people mindlessly swing a blade?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0bb3",
      "back_en": "as a candy vendor to fight crime?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0c90",
      "back_en": "The true voice of the people.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0cdf",
      "back_en": "their mind in front of the real you...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'à frente do você real' desajeitado; preferir 'diante do verdadeiro você'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0d63",
      "back_en": "a simple, harmless candy vendor.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0e80",
      "back_en": "sees that smile of his.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0ed5",
      "back_en": "an ordinary colleague after all.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'fellow' = sujeito/cara, não 'colega' (colleague)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0f20",
      "back_en": "so far, like a fisherman who landed a big catch.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a0f82",
      "back_en": "you really are, too.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel (fragmento)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1023",
      "back_en": "I-I-I-I will defeat you!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a106f",
      "back_en": "behind my back again.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a10b1",
      "back_en": "cowering behind someone's back.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1107",
      "back_en": "collar and hand her towards Mikazuchi.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1df6",
      "back_en": "I look at the man standing there with arms crossed.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1e28",
      "back_en": "Sorry for the delay, ladies and gentlemen!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1e83",
      "back_en": "Oshtor, now as Ukon, enters the room",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Omite 'proudly' (orgulhosamente/com orgulho)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1f80",
      "back_en": "An awkward silence falls as everyone observes the change.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'we'→'todos' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a1fb5",
      "back_en": "Now it's worse, knowing who's underneath",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Adaptação de fragmento ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a2274",
      "back_en": "So it's only okay when HE does it.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a22ce",
      "back_en": "Well, you have a point. Oshtor wouldn't wear",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a2704",
      "back_en": "Ack!? P-I ask, a moment of consideration...!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a27be",
      "back_en": "M-Without a doubt...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Most likely' = 'muito provável', não 'Sem dúvida'; e letra P- não casa com 'Sem'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1a2870",
      "back_en": "stares at me with empty eyes and mutters...",
